name: Zoe Voss
description:
A TI of retired pornstar and former fashion model Zoe Voss.

Updated with two versions trained for longer on more images including full body ones.

modelVersions.name: v3.0
modelVersions.description:
Trained on the same 69 images as v2.0, but with 12 vectors per token instead of 2, learning rate of 0.0015. Best results obtained at 18,000 steps.

I'm very happy with this - it needs far less 'steering' with prompts. Almost all pics I generated were recognisably her, about 1 in 5 are spot on.

Tests produced good results in most realistic models (Ares is the exception), with superb results in Cyberrealistic, Deliberate, DeliberateRealistic and RealisticVision. My preference is for CFG 10 with this TI, YMMV.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Updated with a version trained for longer on more images including full body ones.

69* images

11,000 steps

Embedded learning rate of 0.0025

*Nice.

Still helps to push it with prompts such as '(high cheekbones)' and 'skinny', but the addition of images of her body to the training data reduces this.

Despite the NSFW nature of the training images of her body, NSFW images are surprisingly hard to produce, so perhaps steer it with SFW/NSFW in the +ve/-ve
